data.description:
Welcome to this immaculate 3-bedroom, 2-bath gem nestled in the heart of Broken Arrow! Better than new construction! This home exudes modern charm and offers a spacious open-concept living area flooded with natural light. The well-appointed kitchen boasts sleek granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, perfect for culinary enthusiasts.

The primary bedroom is a tranquil retreat with an ensuite bath featuring a luxurious soaking tub and separate shower. Two additional bedrooms offer ample space for family, guests, or a home office. Additionally, the sellers are leaving the new homeowner's with all of the security equipment which includes the panel, 3 cameras, doorbell camera, motion sensors for the garage door and backdoor, smart wifi thermostat, and keyless entry front door. 

Step outside to the private backyard oasis, ideal for entertaining or relaxation with its amazing extended patio! Enjoy the convenience of a two-car garage and the peace of mind of a well-maintained, move-in-ready home.

Located in the heart of Broken Arrow, you're just moments away from shopping, dining, parks, and top-rated schools. Don't miss this opportunity to make this beautiful property your forever home
